title: Wisconsin
prompt: A wide-angle photograph of a rural Wisconsin county road stretching toward the horizon at golden hour, with weathered fence posts and open farmland under soft amber light, a pickup truck parked on the shoulder with its tailgate down, hands resting on the truck bed edge in the foreground—out of focus but present—suggesting quiet contemplation of vast land and distance; warm earth tones dominating the palette with deep greens and rust-colored fields, the sky pale and overcast, conveying the scale of rural dispersal and the texture of agricultural life without sentimentality.
